reviewText: this is a very fine GENESIS CONERT on DVD , but please don't ever pay more than $20 for an original. the current asking price of almost $400 ripoff.do you wear visit youtube you will find the concert available for free..
Maybe the best Genesis show ever. Enjoyed every second, worth every dollar.

A must have for "old" Genesis fans. OK so no Peter Gabriel...it's still awesome!
Old style progressive rock. Great quality, considering the year it was filmed.
